title: Railworks TS2014 DT Great British Wagon Pack 2
description:
A selection of wagons from the late steam/early diesel era of British railways and LMS period.

LMS 20 Ton Brake in Bauxite
BR 20 Ton Brake in Grey
12 Ton Mineral PO Wagon
12 Ton Mineral PO Wagon with End Doors
8 Ton Drop Side
12 Ton Drop Side
Double Tank Wagon
10 Ton Open
Conflat B, BD, AF
Custom Sounds
Wagon Loads
